fields.review: Eleni helped me break free from generational patterns that I never realized were affecting my life so deeply. Her insights and gentle approach allowed me to see my struggles from a new perspective. I have gained so much emotional freedom through her sessions.

From our first session, I felt a deep sense of trust with Eleni. She has an incredible way of making you feel heard and understood. Through her guidance, I found clarity about my relationships and the courage to make necessary changes. This experience has been one of the most meaningful journeys of my life.

Eleni's approach to systemic therapy helped me reconnect with parts of myself that I had long ignored. She guided me through deep emotions with kindness and patience, allowing me to see my family's influence in a new light. I feel stronger and more at peace, and for that, I am truly grateful.

Eleni has a rare ability to blend professionalism with deep empathy. Her insights helped me heal old wounds and step into a more authentic version of myself. Every session with her was a breakthrough moment.

Eleni’s sessions felt like a revelation. She guided me with patience and understanding, helping me see how my past was shaping my present. Her ability to create a space where I felt completely safe to open up was invaluable.

I came to Eleni feeling lost and stuck in old cycles. Her warmth and expertise helped me untangle deep-seated issues with my family and understand how they were affecting my choices. I now feel a sense of freedom I never thought possible.

Eleni has an incredible gift. She listens deeply, asks the right questions, and helps you connect the dots in ways that feel both profound and natural. Our sessions gave me the tools to break long-standing patterns in my family relationships. I feel more at peace than I have in years.

Working with Eleni was life-changing. She created such a safe and nurturing space for me to explore deep-seated family patterns I hadn’t even realized were holding me back. Her empathy and intuition made me feel truly seen, and I left every session feeling lighter and more empowered. I can’t recommend her enough!

I was skeptical about systemic therapy at first, but Eleni's compassionate and insightful approach won me over completely. She helped me understand my relationships in a way I never had before. Her guidance gave me clarity and a renewed sense of self-worth.
